riptions/ecps.cfm?link=eCPS_quikLink."[6] Phansalker S, Desai AA, Bell D, et al "High-priority drug-drug interactions for use in electronic health records." J Am Med Inform Assoc 19 (2012): 735-43[7] "Product Information. Camptosar (irinotecan)." Pharmacia and Upjohn, Kalamazoo, MI.[8] "Product Information. Juxtapid (lomitapide)." Aegerion Pharmaceuticals Inc, Cambridge, MA.', 1767365207);
